 238:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****  * priority, but the waiting task times out, then the holder should
 239:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****  * disinherit the priority - but only down to the highest priority of any
 240:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****  * other tasks that are waiting for the same mutex.  This function returns
 241:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****  * that priority.
