2551:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****         /* If the queue is already full we may have to block.  A critical section
2552:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****          * is required to prevent an interrupt removing something from the queue
2553:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****          * between the check to see if the queue is full and blocking on the queue. */
